# Spanish Tortilla

## Ingredients

- 12 eggs
- 6-7 big potatoes
- Salt
- Onions


## Instructions

- Cut the potatoes and fry them in olive oil until tender
- Add chopped onions and cook until golden
- Whisk 12 eggs
- Mix the potatoes into the whisked eggs
- Add salt
- Let it simmer for 15-20 mins
- Cook in a clean pan until golden brown
